{
  "stem": "7414.7",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And every time when somebody looked at me, I said to myself, he recognize me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He thinks something.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I-- I-- I have black hair.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was every time, when I had to go out, I looked at myself in the mirror and thought to myself, if I would have light hair, if I would be taller, if my nose would be shorter.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I could not change that, so I had to live as I was.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we lived like that a few months.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Around June, July, we started to hear noises about the uprising is preparing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In our circles, we heard that more than noises.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But the Russian were advancing, and they were deep into Poland, and they got as far as that part of Warsaw which was over the Vistula.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The Vistula was a dividing Warsaw in two parts.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Prague was like a suburb, a big suburb.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they stood there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They did not advance.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We were under the Germans, still they had a very strong grip on us still, and the Russian stood there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Then the Polish government, in exile, decided that it is time to start fighting because they want to free Warsaw, and not the Russian.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So the first of August 1944 it started.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And it started not far from our house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "To first shot were shot from not far from our house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We had to go into the cellar because the Germans were throwing at us everything what they had.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And so it was summer, full summer, August, hot summer.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I had, again, my coat, which I had the loose coat on and light sun dress, and I took the baby and the necessities.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We went to the cellar.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
